# app/instructions.ai
# Responsibility: Main application code for the Network Simulation Server.
# Contains all core logic, API endpoints, models, services, database integration, utilities, logging, and background workers.
# Subfolders:
# - api/: FastAPI route definitions and API logic
# - core/: Core application logic and settings
# - db/: Database integration and MongoDB access
# - logger/: Logging configuration and utilities
# - models/: Pydantic models and data schemas
# - services/: Business logic and simulation management
# - utils/: Utility functions and helpers
# - workers/: Background workers (e.g., RabbitMQ consumers) 